performances.name: Shi*Wrecked, Under The Sea
performances.description: Wash ashore! Come visit the dark depths that live near the lighthouse for Strange Maine's annual Thursday night gathering. Dance to Goth/Industrial and all things Dark, meet some Mainers and hang out in the Lighthouse. Alcoholic and Non alcoholic drinks will be available.
